title: Was Donald Trump's "Baraco Clintizes " famous star's walk poisoned?
subtitle: Donald Trump "Star Fame March" was sabotaged in July 2018, but the man responsible for this was not "Barco Clintiz."
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: A man named Baraco Clintis was responsible for the sabotage of Donald Trump's star on the Hollywood fame march.
